/**
 * Author(s): Dustin Grau (dugrau@progress.com)
 *
 * Obtains table lock info and running programs against a PASOE instance.
 * Usage: getLocks.p <params>
 *  Parameter Default/Allowed
 *   Scheme   [http|https]
 *   Hostname [localhost]
 *   PAS Port [8810]
 *   UserId   [tomcat]
 *   Password [tomcat]
 *   ABL App  [oepas1]
 *
 */

block-level on error undo, throw.

